Class DelimitedReader

java.lang.Object
  org.openadaptor.auxil.connector.iostream.EncodingAwareObject
      org.openadaptor.auxil.connector.iostream.reader.string.DelimitedReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataReader
public class DelimitedReader
extends EncodingAwareObject
implements IDataReader

This class reads string records based on a fixed sequence of delimiter characters. It's delimiter / delimiter char codes property must be configured. The includeDelimiter property controls whether the delimiter characters are included in the record.

perryj
